 made lake based on the confluence of the North and South Opuha Rivers, to the east of Fairlie. The lake was formed behind a dam constructed in 1992 as an irrigation reservoir and small hydro electric plant. The resultant lake formed is now predominately used for recreational water activities such as fishing, boating and water skiing.\",\"Public access to AZ exists:\nVia unformed legal road(s)\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0555,true", "NZLL-0557,Lake Oraekomiko,Manawatū-Whanganui,MW,175.163069,-40.04841,,\"Feature shown on: NZMS260 R23 S23 Edition 1 1986\",\"Accessible only via private land with landowner consent\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0557,true", "NZLL-0561,Lake Otamangakau,Manawatū-Whanganui,MW,175.621,-39.001028,,\"Feature shown on: NZMS260 T19 Edition 2 1994\",\"Accessible only via private land with landowner consent\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0561,true", "NZLL-0562,Lake Otamatearoa,Waikato,WK,174.685896,-37.295749,,\"Feature shown on: NZMS260 Q12 R12 Edition 2 1995\",\"Public access to AZ exists:\nVia public road(s):\nWhiriwhiri Road; 2 unnamed road(s)\n\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0562,true", "NZLL-1083,The Reservoir,Southland,SL,169.060571,-46.655692,,\"Feature shown on: NZMS260 F47 Edition 1 1984\",\"Public access to AZ exists:\nVia park(s):\nConservation Area - The Resevoir, HaldaneVia unformed legal road(s)\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-1083,true", "NZLL-0563,Lake Otapuiti,Northland,NL,174.073364,-36.359876,,\"Accepted feature has no description; to be captured at a later date\",\"Public access to AZ exists:\nVia park(s):\nPouto Wildlife Refuge; Pouto Conservation Area\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0563,true", "NZLL-0455,Lake Mangatutara,Bay of Plenty,BP,177.897767,-37.891173,,\"Feature shown on: NZMS260 Y15 Edition 1 1983 Reprinted 1995\",\"Public access to AZ exists:\nVia park(s):\nRaukumara Conservation Park; Raukumara Wilderness Area\",https://ontheair.nz/assets/NZLL-0455,true", "NZLL-0570,Lake Pan,Southland,SL,167.0